skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: what's up
des: Next time you're trying to decide whose turn it is do chores or perform a task, Or just trying to bust out jokes on the family. Just ask Alexa "What's up" ? For example, you want to tell your wife she looks beautiful? Or say something to your husband. If you're trying to decide whose turn to vacuum the living room. Alexa can randomly select a jokester ,aka "family member" from your secret list. Or if you're wanting to bust on you teen age son or daughter, Alexa can help with that too!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
